FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://api.spiderlog.net

# Spider Log API
Spider Log API provides services for the Spider Log family, recording the world's spider sightings.

# Group Spiders
Access to Spider resources

## My Spiders [/spiders]
### Get all my spider sightings [GET]
+ Request

    + Header
    
            Authorization: Basic QWxhZGRpbjpvcGVuIHNlc2FtZQ==
        
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "sightedAt" : "2014-08-29T07:00",
