### Create a spider sighting [POST]
+ Request (application/json)

    + Header
    
            Authorization: Basic QWxhZGRpbjpvcGVuIHNlc2FtZQ==
            
    + Body

            {
                "sightedAt" : "2014-08-29T19:00",
                "imageUrl" : "https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/spiderlog-images/uid-19247681/201408/14776091214_4699046e5d_z.jpg",
                "description" : "Spider I saw at home",
                "tags": [
                    "big",
                    "stripy"
                ]
            }

+ Response 201

    + Header

            Location: spiders/123

## Spider [/spiders/{id}]
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `123`) ... Numeric `id` of the spider log.

### Fetch sighting details [GET]
+ Request

    + Header
    
            Authorization: Basic QWxhZGRpbjpvcGVuIHNlc2FtZQ==
            
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "sightedAt" : "2014-08-29T19:00",
                "imageUrl" : "https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/spiderlog-images/uid-19247681/201408/14776091214_4699046e5d_z.jpg",
                "description" : "Spider I saw at home",
                "tags": [
                    "big",
                    "stripy"
                ]
            }

### Archive a sighting [DELETE]
+ Request

    + Header
    
            Authorization: Basic QWxhZGRpbjpvcGVuIHNlc2FtZQ==
            
+ Response 204
